                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-btn-sm</code>,
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-btn-md</code>,
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-btn-lg</code> )
                        already includes the base accordion button style and its own padding values.
                        Just put the wanted size class on the button inside
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion</code>
                        or
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-native</code>
                        and the height and inner spacing will adapt automatically.
