                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-body</code>. They are always forced to <code
                            class="text-bold text-primary">0</code>.
                        Add spacing on elements inside the panel (like <code class="text-bold text-primary">p</code> or
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">ul</code>),
                        not on <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-body</code>. Same rule for <code
                            class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion</code> and
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-native</code>.
                    </p>
