                    <p class="p-1">
                        The script listens to clicks on elements with <code class="text-bold text-primary">data-js="collapse"</code>.
                        It reads <code class="text-bold text-primary">data-target</code>, finds the matching <code
                            class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-body</code>,
                        and adds or removes <code class="text-bold text-primary">.show</code>. The open/close animation
                        is 300ms.
                        Extra clicks are ignored during the animation.
                    </p>
                </div>
